{"word":"G569 - ἀπιστέω - apistéō - ap-is-teh'-o - Believe not","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπιστέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apistéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-is-teh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Believe not</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நம்பாமலிரு, விசுவாசியாமலிரு, உண்மையில்லாதிரு"},{"paragraph":"to betray a trust, be unfaithful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G571 - ἄπιστος - ápistos - ap'-is-tos/571\">G571</a>; to <i>be unbelieving</i>, that is, (transitively) <i>disbelieve</i>, or (by implication) <i>disobey:</i> - believe not.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3640/3640\">G3640</a>, <a href=\"#/G4100/4100\">G4100</a>, <a href=\"#/G4102/4102\">G4102</a>, <a href=\"#/G4103/4103\">G4103</a>, <a href=\"#/G4104/4104\">G4104</a>, <a href=\"#/G569/569\">G569</a>, <a href=\"#/G570/570\">G570</a>, <a href=\"#/G571/571\">G571</a>"}]}